lyrics:
[Verse]
In a stinky alleyway where trash resides
A vibrant secret grows, hidden from all eyes
Upside down, mushrooms flourish in the street
A magical sight, oh, what a feast

[Chorus]
Oh, the mushrooms tell tales, stories untold
In this eclectic world, their secrets unfold
A vibrant, electric dance amidst the decay
In this traditional alleyway, where mushrooms sway
